@startuml
title State Diagram - RoomBooking Lifecycle

[*] --> RESERVED : booking created\nroom is available for MeetingSlot

RESERVED --> CONFIRMED : class meeting finalized
RESERVED --> CANCELLED : admin cancels booking

CONFIRMED --> CANCELLED : meeting cancelled\nor room changed
CONFIRMED --> CONFIRMED : view booking history

CANCELLED --> [*]
CONFIRMED --> [*]

note right of RESERVED
Creation requires:
Room.isAvailable(MeetingSlot) == true.
end note

note right of CANCELLED
Cancelled booking stays in history.
The ClassMeeting may remain scheduled,
cancelled, or moved to another room.
end note

note bottom
Qualified association:
Room [MeetingSlot] -> RoomBooking.
MeetingSlot = date + startTime + endTime.
end note

@enduml
